line_1: And every field depriv'd of every sheaf!
line_2: And view the trees disrob'd of every leaf,

line_1: Here half an Acre's Corn is half a Sheaf,
line_2: Here Moss-grown Trees expand the smallest Leaf,

line_1: Hardy and high, above the slender sheaf,
line_2: The slimy mallow waves her silky leaf;
